Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.34,0:02:56.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Mark XI的状态呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.47,0:02:59.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在正在保护运输舰队
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.41,0:03:01.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目前我还没办法回去
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.96,0:03:18.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飞翔 - 牺牲
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.33,0:03:23.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,45区地面受害范围扩大
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.37,0:03:25.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加强防卫机制
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.97,0:03:27.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阻挡它的行动！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.63,0:03:52.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌人到达亚尔维斯装甲外墙
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.97,0:04:01.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,B1-45区块中弹
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.31,0:04:07.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目标持续朝正下方攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.85,0:04:12.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它的目标是女神之岩吗！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.83,0:04:29.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女神之岩似乎启动了专用防壁
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.57,0:04:35.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.15,0:04:49.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又有四架诺伦被击落了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.22,0:04:52.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无法阻止人面狮身型的前进
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.60,0:05:03.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,D9-8区块发生火灾 启动消防系统
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.80,0:05:09.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定会保护你的归宿
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.01,0:05:11.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.83,0:05:33.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一骑…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.60,0:05:38.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定要回来喔
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.14,0:05:42.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就约好罗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.65,0:05:51.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,B3已封闭至第25区块
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.78,0:05:54.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诺伦进入波状攻击体制
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.35,0:05:57.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女神之岩正上方已被破坏至第9区块
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.92,0:06:02.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第18 24 26号自律迎击系统没有反应
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.73,0:06:06.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,命中人面狮身型 但是并没有消灭它
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.16,0:06:07.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,翔子！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.50,0:06:09.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.23,0:06:11.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么穿上协同作用服？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.14,0:06:17.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在打什么主意？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.18,0:06:20.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快说啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.68,0:06:22.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要去跟它战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.58,0:06:25.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别说傻话了！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.58,0:06:29.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也想要保护这座岛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.89,0:06:32.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能让你为了这座岛而去冒这种险啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.76,0:06:34.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并不是为了这座岛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.69,0:06:37.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是为了一骑啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.96,0:06:43.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一骑 使用伏狼刀索！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.18,0:06:53.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.55,0:07:06.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,翔子 你的身体太虚弱了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.22,0:07:07.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从一开始就根本是不可能的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.93,0:07:14.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们不是打从出生就注定要战斗了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.73,0:07:19.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想以我自己的意愿去战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.51,0:07:26.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种小事应该能被允许吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.15,0:07:33.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正我又不是你的孩子…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.65,0:07:38.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从今天起她就是你的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.72,0:07:40.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢您
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.97,0:07:53.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我跟一骑已经约定好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.17,0:07:58.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想要遵守我的诺言
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.50,0:08:58.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟一骑承受一样的痛楚…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.41,0:09:05.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么会启动？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.54,0:09:09.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,羽佐间 是谁启动Mark VI的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.95,0:09:11.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,羽佐间！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.92,0:09:16.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？要出动Mark VI？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.79,0:09:19.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求求你阻止翔子吧 皆城
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.56,0:09:23.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皆城！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.30,0:09:27.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,翔子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.33,0:09:30.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保护这座岛是我们的任务
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.70,0:09:35.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且羽佐间翔子是最适合驾驶Mark VI的人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.44,0:09:39.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您也很清楚吧 羽佐间老师
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.81,0:09:41.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.75,0:09:46.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,羽佐间 出动了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.35,0:09:49.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你 皆城
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.97,0:10:10.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Mark VI？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.24,0:10:12.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,驾驶员是谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.11,0:10:18.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.95,0:10:23.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的是…翔子吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.77,0:10:40.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小楯先生！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.17,0:10:41.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,推进动力平衡有问题
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.27,0:10:45.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让Mark VI暂时回航
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.64,0:10:47.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要重新调整推进引擎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.61,0:10:50.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 真壁！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.01,0:10:52.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有那个必要
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.42,0:10:54.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请您住口
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.55,0:10:58.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不准对大人下令！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.20,0:11:13.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚尔维斯内部受损扩大到B4-86区块
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.17,0:11:17.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Mark VI从上空接近！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.95,0:11:24.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,翔子！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.09,0:11:37.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在那里吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.83,0:11:42.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在那里吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.85,0:12:34.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样如何！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.54,0:12:54.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.64,0:12:56.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一骑 马上回来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.27,0:12:57.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚尔维斯危险了！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.65,0:13:10.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是API-1法夫那的力量？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.81,0:13:40.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我滚出一骑的岛！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.65,0:13:46.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,羽佐间 战斗匕首是没有用的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.22,0:14:13.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,脑波开始产生混乱了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.22,0:14:15.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,翔子！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.95,0:14:17.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Mark VI也行不通吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.41,0:14:46.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没用的羽佐间 羽佐间！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.75,0:15:23.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想要做什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.55,0:15:27.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要把它从这座岛上拉开
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.60,0:15:44.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 在上空就交给诺伦攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.96,0:16:02.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经可以了 快离开异界体
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.83,0:16:06.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么了 羽佐间？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.56,0:16:09.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-我甩不开…\N-什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.21,0:16:19.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赶快逃离啊 羽佐间！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.85,0:16:27.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皆城…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.25,0:16:30.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要使用“魔狼”了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.32,0:16:34.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,密码认证通过 魔狼启动
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.49,0:16:39.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,羽佐间…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.26,0:16:42.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无法执行魔狼解除密码
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.97,0:16:48.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一骑 我会保护你的岛…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.48,0:16:58.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,翔子…为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.92,0:17:01.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一骑…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.49,0:17:08.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总士 这到底是怎么回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.52,0:17:10.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要做傻事啊 翔子！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.98,0:17:29.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皆城…把翔子还给我…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.81,0:17:33.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-甲洋！\N-春日井
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.65,0:17:36.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,候补驾驶员都必须待命
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.02,0:17:38.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不准擅自离开工作岗位
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.59,0:17:43.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.46,0:17:44.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,翔子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.96,0:17:46.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真矢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.24,0:18:01.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,翔子…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.71,0:18:33.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魔狼解放等级设定为最高
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.11,0:18:37.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,羽佐间…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.12,0:18:47.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,翔子！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.13,0:18:53.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,翔子…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.57,0:19:04.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈…妈妈…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.41,0:19:08.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对 妈妈 是妈妈喔
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.71,0:19:10.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.65,0:19:13.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.56,0:19:24.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈 为什么我叫做翔子呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.59,0:19:28.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我希望你能在天空翱翔啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.66,0:19:30.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,翱翔？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.20,0:19:32.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是在天上飞的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.94,0:19:35.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这片天空中翱翔吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.67,0:19:39.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.45,0:19:47.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正我又不是你的孩子…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.95,0:19:53.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 我不该那样说的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.59,0:19:56.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.00,0:20:07.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我这样…有遵守约定了吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.74,0:20:09.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一骑…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.70,0:20:43.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在…是怎样了？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.51,0:20:49.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Mark VI…跟异界体…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.41,0:20:51.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起消灭了…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.37,0:21:18.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是骗人的吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.24,0:21:22.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不是真的吧…翔子…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.51,0:21:26.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌人消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.78,0:21:32.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟贵重的Mark VI一起消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.12,0:21:35.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会这样…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.80,0:21:46.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抬起头来看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.74,0:21:52.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那天虽然晴朗却下了场雨
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.41,0:22:03.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然而她轻轻撑开笑容的伞 递给被雨淋湿的我们
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.59,0:22:09.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并且说着“天空啊 别再哭泣了…”
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.26,0:00:00.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.26,0:00:00.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.26,0:00:00.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.13,0:23:23.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,消失在空中的少女
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.80,0:23:26.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,急于战斗的少年
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.67,0:23:29.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,表现出愤怒的是大人
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.44,0:23:34.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而流下泪来的也是大人
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.25,0:23:39.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,孩子们只是被绝望的雨淋湿
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.45,0:23:44.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集“苍穹之战神”第7话
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.95,0:23:46.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,家贼 - 亲子
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.19,0:23:49.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在那里吗？
